WEBVTT

00:40.953 --> 00:43.782
[thunder rumbling]

00:55.403 --> 00:56.447
[blows air]

00:59.929 --> 01:03.324
[thunder continues rumbling]

01:13.160 --> 01:14.378
[door opens]

01:54.157 --> 01:56.420
[thunder rumbling]

01:56.464 --> 02:00.337
[rain falling]

02:19.791 --> 02:21.053
[thunderclap]

02:26.189 --> 02:27.625
[thunderclap]

02:37.896 --> 02:39.376
[siren whoops]

02:44.686 --> 02:47.732
[radio chatter]

02:57.960 --> 02:59.004
Jake.

02:59.527 --> 03:01.093
Dutch.

03:01.137 --> 03:03.270
Hey, you'’re not gonna
like this one, Jake.

03:03.313 --> 03:04.662
Trust me.

03:05.533 --> 03:08.013
[radio chatter]

03:22.245 --> 03:25.248
[jingling]

03:45.399 --> 03:47.009
[Jake]
Don'’t examine the body

03:47.052 --> 03:50.142
