don'’t mean he can't lie, Mary.

04:21.957 --> 04:23.524
Sage.

04:24.264 --> 04:25.482
Jake!

04:26.353 --> 04:27.354
Wait here.

04:31.967 --> 04:34.535
I already spoke
with Dr. Loesch.

04:34.578 --> 04:37.146
The Artist is right
where he should be.

04:37.189 --> 04:40.367
Just wait till CSI
finish this report.

04:40.410 --> 04:43.718
Can'’t start jumping
into conclusions here.

04:55.991 --> 04:58.080
What were you guys
talking about?

05:00.735 --> 05:02.998
Just some old demons.

05:09.570 --> 05:12.137
[sirens wailing]

05:21.277 --> 05:22.757
[door opens]

05:22.800 --> 05:25.847
St. Joseph'’s
called again today.

05:29.459 --> 05:33.115
The doctors are
giving him one week,
maybe two at the most.

05:34.116 --> 05:35.465
You should go see him.

05:37.119 --> 05:39.817
-I can'’t handle that.
-Mary, this is your dad.

05:39.861 --> 05:42.167
Can we please just
not talk about this?

05:49.044 --> 05:51.481
[recording]
Before the biblical God
created the world,

05:51.525 --> 05:54.092
he first created the heavens.

05:54.136 --> 05:57.226
And inside the heavens,
he created the cherubim,

05:57.269 --> 05:59.315
the angels and the archangels.

05:59.359 --> 06:03.145
The archangels were essentially
the highest rank of angels

06:03.188 --> 06:05.756
and the chief messengers
of God himself.

06:05.800 --> 06:11.371
Among those archangels
was a being known as Lucifer.

06:16.419 --> 06:18.987
[sheriff] Both women
were coated in
a resinous substance.

06:19.030 --> 06:23.295
The lab confirmed
it'’s the same compound
used on previous victims.

06:23.339 --> 06:24.601
Previous victims?

06:24.645 --> 06:26.255
I think it'’s pretty safe
to assume

06:26.298 --> 06:28.866
-we have a copycat
on our hands here, folks.
-Sir?

06:28.910 --> 06:31.434
One with a rather
intimate knowledge
of his predecessor.

06:31.478 --> 06:33.610
-Uh, excuse me, Sheriff?
-Yes, Detective Kelly.

06:33.654 --> 06:36.221
I didn'’t realize that
there were other murders
connected to this case.

06:36.265 --> 06:38.354
I assumed Jake filled you in.

06:39.268 --> 06:40.835
It must'’ve slipped his mind.

06:40.878 --> 06:43.403
Okay, here'’s
the Cliff'’s Notes version.

06:43.446 --> 06:46.971
Five years ago,
serial killer Arnaud Lefeuvre,

06:47.015 --> 06:51.149
aka "The Artist,"
abducted and murdered six women.

06:51.193 --> 06:53.064
Prostitutes, sex workers.

06:54.892 --> 06:59.114
First, he poisoned
and preserved them using a ricin
extracted from castor beans.

06:59.157 --> 07:02.509
Then he'’d arrange
and decorate the corpses

07:02.552 --> 07:05.207
in lifelike poses
using metal frames,

07:05.250 --> 07:08.776
leaving them to be found in
various places around the city.

07:08.819 --> 07:12.214
He called them
his "masterpieces."

07:12.257 --> 07:14.477
I do actually remember that.
It was before finals,

07:14.521 --> 07:16.131
so the details
are a little fuzzy.

07:16.174 --> 07:18.263
How did you guys
end up catching him?

07:18.307 --> 07:20.614
Damn fine detective work
is how.

07:22.267 --> 07:25.488
Done by damn fine detectives,
one of whom is sitting
right beside you.

09:08.722 --> 09:09.766
[siren whoops]

09:10.680 --> 09:11.942
[sighs]

09:11.986 --> 09:14.728
[helicopter whirring]

09:14.771 --> 09:17.295
Hey. You might want to ease up
on the caffeine there.

09:17.339 --> 09:18.819
It'’s the only thing
keeping me vertical.

09:18.862 --> 09:21.822
Sleep hasn'’t been
very restful for me lately.

09:21.865 --> 09:25.652
Ah.A railroad worker
found her about an hour ago.

09:25.695 --> 09:28.872
[radio chatter]

09:28.916 --> 09:31.440
[officer] Need to get some
photographs around here.

09:31.483 --> 09:32.746
[Jake sighs]

09:54.550 --> 09:57.771
[sheriff] The city is still
trying to recover from
what happened five years ago.

09:57.814 --> 10:02.253
Last thing we need
is some damn copycat
reenacting this nightmare.

10:02.297 --> 10:04.647
Well, you'’re preaching
to the choir, sir.

10:04.691 --> 10:09.652
Yeah. That'’s why I'm
considering every option.

10:09.696 --> 10:13.438
-No way. Absolutely not.
-Think objectively here, Jake.

10:13.482 --> 10:15.223
He'’s our best chance,
and you know it.

10:15.266 --> 10:17.965
-Nobody would do this, sir.
-Dutch has already volunteered.

10:18.008 --> 10:20.663
-Dutch?
-Okay, sorry. Vo--
Volunteered for what?

10:22.012 --> 10:23.448
The Artist.

10:24.798 --> 10:28.192
He wants to send Dutch
in there to see The Artist.

10:29.541 --> 10:33.154
Oh, well, that'’s a bold move,
um, but worth a shot.

10:33.197 --> 10:35.199
I think that if you
appeal to his ego,

10:35.243 --> 10:38.463
he would resent the fact
that another lesser artist
is copying his work.

10:39.595 --> 10:43.207
But I think Dutch
needs some finesse.

10:44.731 --> 10:46.689
I would send someone else.

10:46.733 --> 10:49.126
Who do you have in mind,
Detective?

10:50.519 --> 10:53.565
Um, you'’re looking at her.

10:53.609 --> 10:56.307
My background is
in psychology, so...

10:56.351 --> 10:58.135
I'’ve read your file, Mary.

10:59.484 --> 11:01.791
Then what do you say?
You won'’t regret this.

11:02.618 --> 11:05.229
Sir, she'’s not ready for this.

11:05.273 --> 11:08.189
You know what?
I'’m actually very capable
of making my own decisions.

11:08.232 --> 11:09.669
Thank you.
I won'’t let you down.

11:14.761 --> 11:17.546
I'’ll call Dr. Loesch,
set it up this afternoon.

11:18.068 --> 11:19.417
Thank you.

11:25.989 --> 11:28.165
I still deserve to be here,
you know.

11:28.209 --> 11:30.559
So don'’t even think about
monopolizing the conversation.

11:30.602 --> 11:32.126
I get to ask
some of the questions.

11:32.169 --> 11:35.999
All of them actually.
I'’m not going in with you.

11:36.043 --> 11:37.435
What do you mean?

11:37.479 --> 11:39.655
Well, The Artist is
only going to play ball

11:39.699 --> 11:41.918
if we could somehow
win his trust.

11:41.962 --> 11:46.880
That would be impossible
with me in the room,
considering our history.

11:46.923 --> 11:49.883
You mean what?
Other than the arrest? Or...

11:49.926 --> 11:54.191
People will remember The Artist
for the way he murdered
and preserved six women.

11:54.235 --> 11:56.716
But he actually took
seven lives.

11:56.759 --> 11:58.630
What are you talking about?

12:03.157 --> 12:07.204
Zeke Anderson.
My partner of 15 years.

12:07.248 --> 12:09.511
And a good friend.

12:09.554 --> 12:13.297
The night we finally
tracked down The Artist,
Zeke was killed.

12:14.908 --> 12:17.649
Jake, I'’m so sorry.
I... I had no idea.

12:18.738 --> 12:20.043
There'’s more.

12:23.090 --> 12:27.398
That night,
