about a bird?

15:08.864 --> 15:11.301
The reason for my visit today
is actually because--

15:11.345 --> 15:13.521
Regarding the copycat,
no doubt.

15:13.564 --> 15:18.439
I presume you'’d hoped
to pick at my brain
on the matter.

15:18.482 --> 15:20.310
Yes, I was--

15:20.354 --> 15:22.878
I was hoping that you
might familiarize yourself
with the case.

15:22.922 --> 15:25.054
If you saw some photos
of the victims,

15:25.098 --> 15:27.578
maybe you would notice
something that could help us.

15:27.622 --> 15:30.451
