16:03.832 --> 16:06.922
I'’m afraid I don't have
the authority to offer you that.

16:06.966 --> 16:11.796
You will have once we show
the authorities something.

16:11.840 --> 16:12.884
May I?

16:33.383 --> 16:36.212
Photographs of my art macabre

16:36.256 --> 16:38.562
can still be seen
on the Internet

16:38.606 --> 16:40.564
if one knows where to look,

16:40.608 --> 16:42.653
and then used
to replicate my work.

16:42.697 --> 16:46.788
So, the suspect could be
literally anyone.

16:46.831 --> 16:49.443
No, not anyone.

16:49.486 --> 16:51.053
The preservative
was a match.

16:51.097 --> 16:53.142
Your formula, it was
sealed by court order.

16:53.186 --> 16:55.231
It was never released
to the public.

16:55.275 --> 16:57.842
So, this copycat,
he knows far more
than he should.

16:57.886 --> 17:02.499
Maybe it was someone
that you knew from your past,
someone that you confided in?

17:04.545 --> 17:07.069
Could you leave
the file with me tonight?

17:07.113 --> 17:09.376
I'’d like to study it in detail.

17:11.117 --> 17:13.423
I'’ll have Dr. Loesch
bring it to your cell.

17:13.467 --> 17:15.556
