is fast approaching.

17:47.544 --> 17:48.589
Thank you, Mary.

17:50.721 --> 17:53.463
I'’ll see
what I can do.

17:53.507 --> 17:57.032
Should you find anything,
Dr. Loesch will provide you
access to a phone.

17:57.076 --> 18:02.385
