the archangel Samael?

18:02.429 --> 18:05.127
Yes, but I outgrew fairy tales.

18:14.658 --> 18:17.008
And then along comes Mary.

18:17.052 --> 18:18.749
[door opens, closes]

18:26.192 --> 18:30.326
