Someone on the inside must
be feeding him information.

18:30.370 --> 18:33.329
What about our case?
Is he willing to help?

18:33.373 --> 18:36.158
-Uh... [sighs]
-What does he want?

18:36.202 --> 18:38.029
He wants his sentence commuted.

18:38.073 --> 18:40.684
-No damn way!
-Okay. He might know something.

18:40.728 --> 18:42.208
Don'’t be naive, Mary.

18:42.251 --> 18:44.166
