the vehicle right now.

20:07.293 --> 20:08.859
I'’m not gonna ask you again.

20:15.170 --> 20:16.389
[knock on window]

20:18.304 --> 20:20.523
Mind unlocking it?Yeah. Sorry.

20:21.568 --> 20:23.047
Thank you.

20:49.857 --> 20:52.860
Not a single print,
trace of DNA.

20:53.904 --> 20:56.037
Same as the others
five years ago.

21:17.885 --> 21:19.800
[guard over intercom]
Yeah, what is it?

21:19.843 --> 21:23.238
Tell Dr. Loesch I need to
speak with Detective Kelly.

21:32.291 --> 21:33.901
You have two minutes.

21:44.651 --> 21:46.870
Did you see that tattoo
