22:27.041 --> 22:28.521
Oh, I will.

22:28.564 --> 22:32.481
But first I want to make
something perfectly clear.

22:32.525 --> 22:37.530
Whatever help I provide
is for you and only for you.

22:38.879 --> 22:42.883
Not for your police friends,
nor anybody else. Understood?

22:44.145 --> 22:45.189
Understood.

22:46.756 --> 22:51.326
Now, the copycat'’s
latest victim,
the crucified girl...

22:52.719 --> 22:56.549
