23:07.516 --> 23:10.084
For her journey
into the afterlife.

23:25.360 --> 23:27.014
Forget something?

23:27.057 --> 23:29.277
Yeah, I need to look
at these wings.

23:34.325 --> 23:36.327
What exactly did he say?

23:36.371 --> 23:39.200
