the support you need.

24:50.489 --> 24:54.536
How about we focus on
catching the copycat
so they both can fry?

25:02.979 --> 25:04.764
Hey, can I ask you
something?

25:06.200 --> 25:08.985
The night The Artist
was arrested,
what happened, exactly?

25:12.598 --> 25:17.777
Jake and Zeke were pursuing
at a high rate of speed
when Jake lost control.

25:17.820 --> 25:20.170
They crashed.
Vehicle caught on fire.

25:20.214 --> 25:22.564
Jake made it out.
Zeke died at the scene.

25:25.436 --> 25:27.569
Jake suffered bad burns
on his left arm,

25:27.613 --> 25:29.832
but he still
made the arrest, Mary.

26:29.196 --> 26:31.372
[The Artist] Hello, Jacob.

26:31.415 --> 26:34.941
I suppose a firm handshake'’s
out of the question.

26:36.159 --> 26:38.509
