27:00.401 --> 27:02.359
he became it.

27:02.403 --> 27:03.752
Oh, yeah?

27:03.796 --> 27:05.624
I didn'’t lay
a finger on him.

27:05.667 --> 27:08.539
Your partner set
himself ablaze.

27:11.934 --> 27:12.979
Jake.

27:16.809 --> 27:17.853
Jake.

27:18.854 --> 27:20.421
Put your firearm down.

27:21.988 --> 27:23.032
Now.

27:32.738 --> 27:34.087
We need to have a talk.

